text: Mansehra is a city in Khyber Pakhtunkhwa, Pakistan. Mansehra may also refer to: *Mansehra District, a district of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa, Pakistan *Mansehra Tehsil, a tehsil of Mansehra district *Mansehra (Rural), a union council in Mansehra District ==See also== *Mansehra Rock Edicts, fourteen rock edicts of Mauryan emperor Ashoka *Mansehra Jihad training camp, an Afghan jihad camp. * *
